    in.

 5. Release the mouse when you have cropped the desired amount of the
    graphic.

 TO RESTORE AN IFF ILBM TO ITS UN-CROPPED SIZE:  See fig 8-2
------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1. Select the graphic to be restored.

 2. Press the ALT key and while holding it down double-click the mouse on
